cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on depth estimation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a deep convolutional neural network (CNN) to learn the affinity matrix for spatial propagation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of the proposed method for stereo matching, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
